reviews.text:
Krucial is too kind! My part was small in this. &#xD;
If you like oatmeal raisin cookies then I have no doubt, this is for you. It's exactly that. FLV pretty much nails the raisin part but needs help with the cookie part. JF Biscuit, with the CDS, does a great job of doing that. JF Bavarian Cream and TFA Butter were the keys to keeping this from being too dry. This worked great without compromising and turning it into a cookies N' Cream recipe. &#xD;
Krucial did a great job on this and I'm honored to be linked to this recipe. This is now in my ADV rotation.
